,{"localized_name":"positive","name":"positive","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"positive"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"positive_token_normalization","name":"positive_token_normalization","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"positive_token_normalization"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"positive_weight_interpretation","name":"positive_weight_interpretation","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"positive_weight_interpretation"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"negative","name":"negative","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"negative"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"negative_token_normalization","name":"negative_token_normalization","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"negative_token_normalization"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"negative_weight_interpretation","name":"negative_weight_interpretation","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"negative_weight_interpretation"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"batch_size","name":"batch_size","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"batch_size"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"a1111_prompt_style","name":"a1111_prompt_style","shape":7,"type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"a1111_prompt_style"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"pipe","name":"pipe","type":"PIPE_LINE","links":[1]},{"localized_name":"model","name":"model","type":"MODEL","links":null},{"localized_name":"vae","name":"vae","type":"VAE","links":null},{"localized_name":"clip","name":"clip","type":"CLIP","links":null},{"localized_name":"positive","name":"positive","type":"CONDITIONING","links":null},{"localized_name":"negative","name":"negative","type":"CONDITIONING","links":null},{"localized_name":"latent","name":"latent","type":"LATENT","links":null}],"title":"1. EasyLoader (Full)","properties":{"Node name for S&R":"easy fullLoader"},"widgets_values":["oneObsession_v22.safetensors","Default","Baked VAE",-2,"None",1,1,"1024 x 1024",768,1152,"masterpiece, best quality, 8k, semi-realistic portrait, hyperdetailed, young japanese woman, feminine soft face, delicate features, long messy white hair pushed back or tucked behind ears, clean hair without markings, pale porcelain skin, skin microdetails, skin macrodetails, intense melancholic dark eyes, heavy subtle shadows under eyes, face covered in rough black ink overlay, hand-drawn kanji calligraphy, X marks, plus symbols, cross-hatching, dry brush strokes, ink splatters directly on cheeks forehead nose and jaw, layered grunge graphic markings on skin NOT tattoos, dark high collar black coat, dramatic top lighting, deep chiaroscuro shadows, high contrast black and white monochrome, raw ink wash aesthetic, cinematic psychological portrait, subtle film grain, shot on 85mm f/1.4, shallow depth of field","none","comfy","score_6, score_5, score_4, deformed, bad anatomy, blurry, lowres, extra limbs, disfigured, watermark, text, signature, worst quality","none","comfy",1,false],"color":"#223","bgcolor":"#335"},{"id":10,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[-757.4342019502013,15.197285518613448],"size":[580,620],"flags":{},"order":0,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"HOW TO USE","properties":{},"widgets_values":["# SDXL Max Quality (EasyUse HiresFix)\n\n**EasyUse chain** :\n`fullLoader` -> `fullkSampler` (base) -> **`HiresFix`** -> `fullkSampler` (refine) -> FaceDetailer -> FINAL\n\n## Main settings\n1. **EasyLoader (Full)** : checkpoint + prompts + base resolution (1024x1024).\n2. **Base sampler** : denoise **1.0** (initial generation).\n3. **HiresFix** : upscale ESRGAN x4 or other upscaler **50%** (= x2 net, like A1111). Ajust `percent` or pass in `to longer side` with `longer_side=1536`.\n4. **Hi-Res sampler** : denoise **0.45** (refine, doesn't break image).\n5. **FaceDetailer** : re-diffuse the face.\n\n## HiresFix - cursors\n- `model_name` : RealESRGAN_x4plus or anything you like.\n- `rescale_after_model` : **True** (for a real hires fix it's necessary).\n- `rescale` + `percent=50` : after a x4, 50% = final image x2.\n- Alternative : `to longer side - maintain aspect` + `longer_side=1536`.\n\n## Z-Image pass (Optional but can enhance details)\n\n## Modeles requis\n-  SDXL Checkpoint in EasyLoader\n- `bbox/face_yolov8m.pt` + `sam_vit_b_01ec64.pth` (FaceDetailer)\n- `RealESRGAN_x4plus.safetensors` or any like UltraSharp or smth (HiresFix)"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"}],"links":[[1,1,0,2,0,"PIPE_LINE"],[2,2,0,3,0,"PIPE_LINE"],[3,3,0,4,0,"PIPE_LINE"],[4,4,0,5,0,"PIPE_LINE"],[5,5,1,8,1,"MODEL"],[6,5,6,8,2,"CLIP"],[7,5,2,8,4,"CONDITIONING"],[8,5,3,8,5,"CONDITIONING"],[9,5,5,8,3,"VAE"],[10,5,7,8,0,"IMAGE"],[11,6,0,8,6,"BBOX_DETECTOR"],[12,7,0,8,7,"SAM_MODEL"],[13,8,0,9,0,"IMAGE"],[14,8,0,17,3,"IMAGE"],[18,13,0,17,2,"VAE"],[19,15,0,17,5,"CONDITIONING"],[20,14,0,17,9,"UPSCALE_MODEL"],[22,17,0,19,1,"IMAGE"],[23,16,0,17,1,"CONDITIONING"],[24,8,0,19,0,"IMAGE"],[25,11,0,20,0,"MODEL"],[26,20,0,17,0,"MODEL"],[27,20,1,15,0,"CLIP"],[28,12,0,20,1,"CLIP"],[29,20,1,16,0,"CLIP"]],"groups":[{"id":1,"title":"EasyUse: Loader + HiresFix","bounding":[-160,-20,1560,620],"color":"#3f789e","flags":{}},{"id":2,"title":"FaceDetailer + Save","bounding":[1400,-20,1240,1026.943506141473],"color":"#88A","flags":{}},{"id":3,"title":"Z-Image polish (OPTIONAL) - Ctrl-B","bounding":[2650.0242536830174,-12.624820672204061,1222.0936118588816,1326.8885258408911],"color":"#a1309b","flags":{}}],"config":{},"extra":{"ds":{"scale":0.7985976785102166,"offset":[-1831.695115035661,261.24975535115857]}},"version":0.4}